BPCL was proud to be a part of the 4th Rosefield Energy Tech Conference on Circular Economy in Used Oil, held recently in Delhi.

Mr. Sarvesh Singh Tomar, General Manager P&AD, actively contributed to a panel discussion, sharing valuable insights on the innovative future of circularity in used oil across India. He emphasised the need for policy reforms like EPR (Extended Producer Responsibility) and stronger industry-wide cooperation to make Re-refined Base Oil (RRBO) a scalable and sustainable reality for the country.

